profile:
our website: http://www.onlyessentials.com/

Your need to survive can be due to bad weather, a 
natural disaster or just the challenge of heading
out into the wilderness. When you are faced with 
nature, you need the highest quality survival gear
you can find that is specific to your needs and 
the environment you live in.
